lex flex-col items-center"><div class="rounded-xl bg-ds-white-white p-ds-5 gap-ds-3 flex h-[56px] cursor-pointer items-center sm:h-[68px] w-[calc(100vw-32px)] max-w-full"><div class="content-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="Search"><path d="M20.25 20.25L16.1265 16.1265M16.1265 16.1265C17.4385 14.8145 18.25 13.002 18.25 11C18.25 6.99594 15.0041 3.75 11 3.75C6.99594 3.75 3.75 6.99594 3.75 11C3.75 15.0041 6.99594 18.25 11 18.25C13.002 18.25 14.8145 17.4385 16.1265 16.1265Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-neutral"></path></svg></div><div class="grow"><input class="text-ds-body1 cursor-pointer outline-none" readonly="" placeholder="Search all"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="!mt-0 flex justify-center px-ds-5 lg:px-ds-9 py-11 md:py-ds-7 md:pb-28"><div class="w-full max-w-[1252px]"><div class="pb-24"><article><div class="mb-ds-7 m-auto max-w-[722px]"><header><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-kraken-24-regular-brand md:text-ds-kraken-36-regular-brand ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0">Linear Multi-Collateral Derivatives Contract Specifications</span></header></div><section><div class="m-auto max-w-[722px]"><div data-article-content="796b9858bbab" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Below you can find three sections with detailed information on Kraken&#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts.<br/></div></div><div data-article-content="6fd96943fc73" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Click to expand each section:</div></div><div data-article-content="9dca416c2057" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1"><div style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0" data-pt="true"><div class="border-t border-[rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04)]"><div class="relative"><div id="85Bl7Ei4pF_CN0GWYSZ59" class="absolute -top-16 h-16"></div><div class="py-ds-5 flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between hover:text-primary outline-primary focus-visible:mx-[1px] focus-visible:pl-[1px] accordion-header" role="button" tabindex="0" data-testid="accordion-item-header"><h5 class="my-ds-0" data-article-nav="85Bl7Ei4pF_CN0GWYSZ59" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-kraken-16-regular ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0">Perpetual Contract Specifications</span></h5><div class="shrink-0 transition-transform" style="width:24px;height:24px;margin-left:16px"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="ChevronDown"><path d="M20 9L13.4142 15.5858C12.6332 16.3668 11.3669 16.3668 10.5858 15.5858L4 9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-dimmed"></path></svg></div></div><div class="max-h-0 border-b border-[rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04)]" data-testid="accordion-item-content"><div class="pb-ds-8 pt-ds-2 hidden"><div style="visibility:hidden;padding-right:40px"><div data-article-content="dGPPrUOir4hlLb3DHjEQq" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have <strong>no expiration date</strong> and an <strong>auto-rolling</strong> feature <strong>every hour</strong>. </div></div><div data-article-content="DiebBMjW3TudjNXGPnSlJ" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. </div></div><div data-article-content="Y_hveZNPp40dj3AI8PsG5" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1"><strong>Margin Class</strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in <a href="/hc/en-us/articles/360022632452-Multi-Collateral-Futures-Margin-Schedule-Maximum-Leverage" class="cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-ds-brand underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-0 hover:text-hover hover:decoration-1 visited:decoration-0" data-testid="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span>Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage</span></a>.</div></div><div data-article-content="Sz65rY3QWhIH2KvoNMQuQ" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="[&amp;_a]:!text-ds-notification-subtitle-primary"><div data-testid="notification-container" aria-labelledby=":R2dn776:" aria-describedby=":R2dn776H1:" class="relative flex min-w-[300px] items-start overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl bg-ds-notification-primary rounded-ds-notification-md p-ds-4 md:items-center text-ds-notification-primary ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 group"><div class="mr-ds-notification-gap-md rounded-ds-round flex size-fit p-1.5 bg-ds-circle-primary" data-testid="leading-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="InfoCircle"><path d="M11 11H12V16M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-primary"></path><rect x="11.5" y="7.5" width="1" height="1" rx="0.5" stroke-width="2" class="fill-ds-icon-primary stroke-ds-icon-primary"></rect></svg></div><div class="flex flex-1 flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-x-3 gap-y-3"><div class="flex flex-col"><span id=":R2dn776:" class="text-ds-kraken-14-medium">Please note:</span><span id=":R2dn776H1:" class="text-ds-kraken-14-regular text-ds-notification-subtitle-primary"><div class="[&amp;_.text-ds-body1]:text-ds-body2"><div style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Delisted and settled contracts are archived <a href="https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings" class="cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-ds-brand underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-0 hover:text-hover hover:decoration-1 visited:decoration-0" data-testid="external-link"><span>here</span></a>. </div></div></div></span></div></div><div class="grid justify-items-end"></div></div></div></div><div data-article-content="84i1MLDuvF1c-dWQwA2yS" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0" data-pt="true"><div class="py-20"><div class="relative overflow-x-auto md:left-[calc((40vw-361px)*-1)] md:w-[80vw]"><table class="mobile-table w-full text-left"><thead class="border-b border-dark min-h-[undefinedpx]"><tr class="border-b border-dark"><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-kraken-16-medium ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><div style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px